-- Credit Suisse May Have to Cut 5,000 Jobs, Der Sonntag Reports
-- B y   C o r i n n e   G r e t l e r
-- 2012-04-15T13:04:42Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-15/credit-suisse-may-have-to-cut-5-000-jobs-der-sonntag-reports.html
Credit Suisse Group AG (CSGN) ,
Switzerland’s second-biggest lender, may have to cut about 5,000
jobs, Der Sonntag reported, citing an unidentified high-ranking
executive, who said its investment bank is “simply oversized.”  To contact the reporter on this story:
Corinne Gretler in Zurich at 
 cgretler1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew Rummer at   arummer@bloomberg.net  